videos.description: Carsen Edwards intercepts a pass and goes all the way to score for Purdue.
videos.headline: Edwards turns steal into layup

videos.description: Dakota Mathias finds a cutting Matt Haarms who dunks for Purdue.
videos.headline: Haarms powers down two-handed jam

videos.description: After Purdue forces a turnover, Vincent Edwards misses a layup but Matt Haarms cleans it up to score and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Haarms hits putback layup plus a foul

videos.description: Carsen Edwards finds a cutting Isaac Haas who throws down a powerful dunk for Purdue.
videos.headline: Haas punishes rim with one-handed jam

videos.description: Dakota Mathias shoots 7-for-9 from behind the ark giving him a new career-high in his last home game for Purdue.
videos.headline: Mathias sets new career-high by hitting 7th 3-pointer
